if you want read diamond one by one and get only the best, you could define the worst `Diamond` (on `Diamond` class)

    static final Diamond WORST = new Diamond(0.0f, 0.0f);

now, reading from _stdin_ you initialize the best diamond and get better when read a new one

    Diamond best = Diamond.WORST;
